descp2: An int or list of `ints` that has length `1`, `N` or `N+2`, defaults to 1. The dilation factor for each dimension of`input`. If a single value is given it is replicated in the spatial dimensions. By default the `N` and `C` dimensions are set to 1. If set to k > 1, there will be k-1 skipped cells between each filter element on that dimension. The dimension order is determined by the value of `data_format`, see above for details.
